  "full_path": "do broker-tenders update",
  "description": "Update a broker tender.",
  "permissions": "Admins or users who are members of the buyer broker; trucker managers with can_see_rates_as_manager may update only seller_operations_contact or seller_financial_contact.",
  "side_effects": "Updates a broker tender record.",
  "validation_notes": "Requires a broker tender ID argument and at least one update flag. expires-at must be RFC3339 when provided. Boolean-like flags (is-trucker-shift-rejection-permitted, restrict-to-customer-truckers, displays-trips) expect 'true' or 'false'. payment-terms must be a number >= 0. buyer must be a Broker and seller must be a Trucker. seller_financial_contact must have a manager trucker membership with the seller; seller_operations_contact must have a membership with the seller; buyer_operations_contact and buyer_financial_contact must have memberships with the buyer. If restrict-to-customer-truckers is true, the seller must be in the customer truckers list; if there are accepted customer tenders, restrict-to-customer-truckers must match their restriction setting.",
